name: Sweet Freedom Card V4
description:
You will receive 1 card (as seen in photo) with matching kraft envelope. 

-Printed on 110 lb white cardstock
-Size: A2 (4.25x5.5)
-Packaged in a clear cello bag


These cards were designed for the Sweet Freedom Campaign to create awareness for the social injustice in the cocoa fields of West Africa.

Sweet Freedom: https://www.facebook.com/pages/Sweet-Freedom-Campaign/352332031453538

+All proceeds from the sale of this card go to Making Noise, Inc. 

Making Noise, Inc is a Washington, DC non-profit organization that aims to use the arts, media, drama, and blogs to raise awareness of social injustice issues in Africa.

http://livethenoise.com
